The link of the created dashboard using Google Data Studio is given below.

https://datastudio.google.com/u/0/reporting/d7bb3d09-f0ce-4588-ba7c-d1e4c68db238/page/nKzuB

The dataset for this dashboard is updated every 15 minutes based on the update from the primary data website https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/

This COVID-19 data is then retrived from this webpage to a google sheet which acts as a data source for the dashboard.

